OL,3,CUK development power diminished since
OL,4,CForeign Office merger, watchdog says
OL,6,FBritain's international development
OL,7,Fpower has diminished since the merging
OL,8,Fof two Government departments into one
OL,9,Fforeign affairs office, the UK's
OL,10,Fpublic spending watchdog has found.
OL,12,FThe loss of dedicated senior roles
OL,13,Foverseas as a result of the change in
OL,14,Fleadership structure has undermined
OL,15,Fcredibility and accountability,
OL,16,Faccording to the National Audit Office
OL,17,F(NAO).
