OL,3,CUK development power diminished since
OL,4,CForeign Office merger, watchdog says
OL,6,FThe findings are part of a report by
OL,7,Fthe watchdog into the progress of the
OL,8,Fmerger of the Foreign & Commonwealth
OL,9,FOffice and the Department for
OL,10,FInternational Development.
OL,12,FThe two departments were were
OL,13,Fcontroversially replaced in 2020 by
OL,14,Fthe Foreign, Commonwealth and
OL,15,FDevelopment Office (FCDO) under the
OL,16,Fleadership of Boris Johnson, who said
OL,17,Fit would deliver better value for
OL,18,Fmoney on aid spending.
