OL,3,CUK development power diminished since
OL,4,CForeign Office merger, watchdog says
OL,6,FThe NAO said the new department has
OL,7,Fmade substantial progress but that
OL,8,Fmore work is needed to clarify
OL,9,Fcapability needs, resolve outstanding
OL,10,FHR and IT issues, and move ahead with
OL,11,Fculture change.
OL,13,FThere are examples where a more
OL,14,Fintegrated approach has improved
OL,15,FFCDO's ability to respond to
OL,16,Finternational crises and events, such
OL,17,Fas the support for delivery of Covid-
OL,18,F19 vaccines across the world during
OL,19,Fthe pandemic, the watchdog said.
