OL,3,CUK development power diminished since
OL,4,CForeign Office merger, watchdog says
OL,6,FHowever, the department does not know
OL,7,Fthe full costs of the merger and has
OL,8,Fchosen not to systematically track its
OL,9,Fbenefits, including cost savings,
OL,10,Forganisational improvements and
OL,11,Fefficiency gains, according to the
OL,12,Freport.
OL,14,FThe NAO said: "FCDO's development
OL,15,Fcapability has reduced since the
OL,16,Fmerger. FCDO has changed leadership
OL,17,Fstructures and roles to integrate
OL,18,Fdevelopment and diplomacy.
