OL,3,CUK development power diminished since
OL,4,CForeign Office merger, watchdog says
OL,6,F"As a consequence, in some overseas
OL,7,Fposts the loss of dedicated senior
OL,8,Fdevelopment roles has reduced capacity
OL,9,Fand undermined FCDO's credibility and
OL,10,Fofficial development assistance (ODA)
OL,11,Faccountability.
OL,13,F"While there has been some replacement
OL,14,Fthrough internal accreditation and
OL,15,Fexternal recruitment, the number of
OL,16,Fexpert development adviser roles fell
OL,17,Fby 14% from 867 in 2019 to 747 in 2022.
