OL,3,CUK development power diminished since
OL,4,CForeign Office merger, watchdog says
OL,6,F"FCDO has also lost development
OL,7,Fcapability around programme management
OL,8,Ffor its ODA programmes, with 25% of
OL,9,Fsuch positions in the major programmes
OL,10,Fportfolio reported as vacant in
OL,11,FJanuary 2024.
OL,13,F"FCDO has been aware of the risk of
OL,14,Fnot sustaining its international
OL,15,Fdevelopment skills and expertise,
OL,16,Fwhich it currently rates as 'severe',
OL,17,Fand is working to mitigate this risk."
