OL,6,FGareth Davies, head of the NAO,
OL,7,Fpraised the Foreign Office for taking
OL,8,F"sensible action" to get the merger
OL,9,Fback on track against a backdrop of
OL,10,Fglobal challenges, including the
OL,11,Fpandemic and geopolitical crises in
OL,12,FAfghanistan and Ukraine.
OL,14,FHe added: "However, more than three
OL,15,Fyears on from the merger, there is
OL,16,Fstill work to do to resolve remaining
OL,17,Fissues, ensure the basics are
OL,18,Fdelivered and achieve the long-term
OL,19,Fbenefits of a fully integrated
OL,20,Fdepartment.
