OL,3,CUK development power diminished since
OL,4,CForeign Office merger, watchdog says
OL,6,F"More broadly, government needs to
OL,7,Funderstand the costs of such major
OL,8,Fchange, including the disruption and
OL,9,Fconsumption of management capacity,
OL,10,Fand weigh these carefully against the
OL,11,Fanticipated benefits."
OL,13,FAid organisations and political
OL,14,Fopponents have repeatedly criticised
OL,15,Fthe Government's decision to fold
OL,16,Finternational development into the
OL,17,FForeign Office, arguing it would
OL,18,Fdamage the effectiveness of Britain's
OL,19,Faid spending.
