OL,6,F"With conflict, climate change and
OL,7,Finequality hurting low-income
OL,8,Fcommunities around the world, we need
OL,9,Fa strong, independent and properly-
OL,10,Fresourced international development
OL,11,Fdepartment that is committed to
OL,12,Fforging partnerships with the global
OL,13,Fsouth and making a real difference in
OL,14,Fthe fight against poverty."
OL,16,FAn FCDO spokesperson said: "The merger
OL,17,Fhas given us the integrated capability
OL,18,Fneeded to grow, and drive our foreign
OL,19,Fpolicy, national security and
OL,20,Finternational development objectives
OL,21,Fin a more effective and joined-up way.
