OL,9,Ftackle crises and further UK interests.
OL,11,F"We know there is more to do, and
OL,12,Fremain committed to the mission of the
OL,13,FFCDO. Our recent actions, such as the
OL,14,Fappointment of a Second Permanent
OL,15,FUnder-Secretary with a focus on
OL,16,Fdevelopment, have allowed us to better
OL,17,Fbring together diplomacy, consular
OL,18,Fsupport and development to achieve
OL,19,Fmore for the UK."
